Class StaffManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • StaffManager

  • public class StaffManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Class hold list of staff and operations only for staffs. Opeartions such as update status of movie, update list of MovieListing, update list of special date and price system and provide authetication for other people.
